1
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:05,250
Think about the best professional you know.

2
00:00:05,760 --> 00:00:08,370
 Maybe it's a manager, a mentor, someone you've worked with.

3
00:00:09,060 --> 00:00:10,700
 What makes them good at what they do?

4
00:00:11,510 --> 00:00:14,150
 Chances are, it's not just that they have the right skills.

5
00:00:14,540 --> 00:00:17,320
 It's that they've learned from experience in a way that most people 

6
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:17,830
don't.

7
00:00:18,430 --> 00:00:20,990
 They can tell you exactly what they'd do differently if they could 

8
00:00:21,020 --> 00:00:24,750
run a meeting again, or why their approach to a particular problem 

9
00:00:24,820 --> 00:00:27,060
changed after seeing it go wrong the first time.

10
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:29,280
 That's reflective practice.

11
00:00:29,790 --> 00:00:32,680
 It's the difference between having ten years of experience and 

12
00:00:32,750 --> 00:00:34,790
having one year of experience ten times.

13
00:00:36,110 --> 00:00:38,440
 In this course, you'll use a model called DEAL.

14
00:00:38,830 --> 00:00:42,020
 Describe what happened. Examine why it happened the way it did.

15
00:00:42,890 --> 00:00:45,290
 Then articulate what you learned and how you'll use it going 

16
00:00:45,360 --> 00:00:49,870
forward. It sounds straightforward, and it is, but it takes practice.

17
00:00:50,930 --> 00:00:53,880
 Most people skip straight from "what happened" to "what I'll do 

18
00:00:53,950 --> 00:00:57,590
next" without spending any time on the examine step, the part 

19
00:00:57,610 --> 00:00:58,860
where the real insight lives.

20
00:00:59,810 --> 00:01:02,760
 You'll complete several DEAL reflections throughout this course.

21
00:01:03,270 --> 00:01:04,910
 Each one builds on the last.

22
00:01:05,350 --> 00:01:08,700
 By the end, you'll have a portfolio that shows not just what you did, 

23
00:01:08,820 --> 00:01:10,290
but what you learned from doing it.

24
00:01:11,090 --> 00:01:14,100
 That's the kind of evidence that stands out in a job interview or a 

25
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:14,970
performance review.